        <p>MR. SPEAKER : Order, please. We'll begin the daily routine.</p>
      </speech>
      <speech by="#03bf943f-63b6-4e10-a49b-62ac3ada194e">
        <from>MR. LARRY HARRISON</from>
        <p>MR. LARRY HARRISON : Mr. Speaker, before tabling a petition, I beg leave to make an introduction.</p>
      </speech>
