        <from>MR. HARRISON</from>
        <p>MR. HARRISON : In the west gallery a number of folks have come today for a petition, and I'll ask them to stand as their name is called. Maura Hunter, Deborah Smith, Ida Kuhn, Joe Hunter, Christine Crowe, Randy Crowe, Bill Smith, George Thomas, Nadine Thomas, Claudia Leclerc, Lloyd Gibbs, Valerie Hollingsworth, Nancy Samson; and from Kings County, Chris Conn, Warren Peck, and Dick Killam. (Applause)</p>
      </speech>
